title: 107_hr4723
content: Authorizes the President to extend nondiscriminatory treatment to the products of the Ukraine. Declares that it is the policy of the United States to remain fully committed to a multifaceted engagement with the Ukraine, including by: (1) urging the Ukraine to continue its policy of providing for the free emigration of its citizens and recognizing human rights. And (2) ensuring that Ukraine's terms of accession to the World Trade Organization provide meaningful market access opportunities for US businesses, farmers, and workers.
